data-mesh-id="Cntnr4inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="Cntnr4inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><div id="WRchTxtl" class="_1Z_nJ" data-testid="richTextElement"><h5 class="alignLeft    font_5" style="line-height:1.2em;text-align:center;font-size:25px"><span><span class="color_11">Welcome to Butte County, South Dakota!</span></span></h5>
</div></div></div></div><div id="mainPage_WRichText_5" class="_1Z_nJ" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="alignLeft   font_8" style="font-size:14px; line-height:1.3em"><span style="font-size:14px">Butte County was named from the numerous buttes which rise abruptly from the prairies in the area.<br />
The county seat is in Belle Fourche, which is also known as the &quot;Center of the Nation.&quot; Our county was established in the state of South Dakota on March 2, 1883. The name Belle Fourche came from the French explorers and means &quot;beautiful fork.&quot; You can learn more about the history of our community&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration:underline;"><a href="http://www.thetristatemuseum.com/history-of-belle-fourche/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a></span>.</span></p></div><div id="comp-iyosrk0b" class="_2TxBB" title=""><div data-testid="linkElement" class="_2yXCL"><wix-image id="img_comp-iyosrk0b" class="_1SQyl DFk41" data-image-info="{&quot;containerId&quot;:&quot;comp-iyosrk0b&quot;,&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;,&quot;imageData&quot;:{&quot;width&quot;:1366,&quot;height&quot;:768,&quot;uri&quot;:&quot;23b983_569d9160188e421faa4857c976d855a4~mv2.jpg&quot;,&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;,&quot;crop&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:213,&quot;y&quot;:0,&quot;width&quot;:943,&quot;height&quot;:764}}}" data-bg-effect-name="" data-is-svg="false" data-is-svg-mask="false" data-image-zoomed=""><img alt="Butte County SD Courthouse"/></wix-image></div></div><div id="Cntnr6"><div class="_3wcxZ"></div><div class="_3TwMx"></div><div class="_2k5dr"></div><div data-mesh-id="Cntnr6inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="Cntnr6inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><div id="mainPage_WRichText_8" class="_1Z_nJ" data-testid="richTextElement"><h5 class="font_5" style="line-height:1.2em;text-align:center;font-size:25px"><span><span class="color_11">Important Information</span></span></h5>
